References
==========

 * Archlinux.org
   Wiki.archlinux.org

 * i3wm.org

 * https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/VirtualBox#Launch_the_VirtualBox_guest_services
   This tells you how to make virtualbox arch work, incl. X11.

   example .xinitrc
```
/usr/bin/VBoxClient-all
exec gnome-session
```
